      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "that makes sense. so with lasso, the way it just zeros out certain things... is there a mathematical reason why it goes all the way to zero while ridge just gets really small? like what's happening with the geometry of it?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
